Present the Black Sacrament token to Delvin └─→ Delvin provides everything in his topic table above. Free. Professional courtesy. └─→ Parting line: "One thing. When it's done — however it's done — the Guild needs the pipeline to continue. Constance takes over. The kids keep training. If that arrangement holds, nobody asks questions. If it doesn't..." He shrugs. "Maven asks questions. You don't want Maven asking questions."
