EXIT
Party has Flagon intelligence. Time is passing. Proceed to Scene 3 (the Warrens) via the descending tunnel behind the Flagon. Key info gained: Thalmor 30 min ahead, Esbern's location confirmed, Grelod intelligence (if Orion pursued it), the Warrens are populated and the Thalmor left a mess going through. Likely next: Scene 3 (The Warrens).

