THE INVESTIGATION: CAIUS VARRO'S SATCHEL
The dead Blades agent's satchel contains two critical items:
ITEM 1: Caius's Letter to Esbern (undelivered)
A sealed letter. The seal is a stylized diamond shape — the mark of the Blades.
"Esbern — I have found it. Sky Haven Temple is real. The Karthspire entrance is intact, hidden behind a Forsworn camp in the Reach. Alduin's Wall is inside — the complete prophecy, carved in stone by the Akaviri themselves. Everything we theorized is confirmed. The Wall describes a Shout that can force a dragon from the sky. But there is more — the Wall depicts something we did not expect. A council. A gathering of heroes who are not Dragonborn. The Akaviri foresaw a world where the Dragonborn fails. They prepared for it. We need to reach the Temple. I am coming to you. We go together. — C.V."
What this gives the party:
Category
Information
Location
Sky Haven Temple, accessed through the Karthspire in the Reach
Contents
Alduin's Wall — a complete prophecy carved in stone
The Shout
A Shout exists that can ground dragons (Dragonrend)
The Revelation
The Akaviri prepared for a world without the Dragonborn — the party's exact situation
Emotional weight
The man who found this died ten feet from delivering it

